caption.title: Immunoelectron microscopy showing RSV particle entered Sf9 cells.
caption.p: (A) RSV particles and LsST6 colocalized in the cell membrane by 7 h. (B) RSV particles had entered the cytoplasm. (C) Numerous RSV particles were distributed in the cytoplasm. Red arrows: 10-nm gold-conjugated goat anti-rabbit IgG against RSV used to detect virus; yellow arrows: 5-nm gold-conjugated goat anti-mouse IgG against LsST6.
